<br>
Getting to Katta at level 34 is a little nervy. You need to go thru Fungus(not recomended) or grimling and tenebrous. Invis is useless in Tenebrous. Recomend a sow, stay high on the wall and run. Also good to have printed maps so you know where your headed as Grimling and Tenebrous are on the dark side of the moon.<br>
<br>
