<br>
Click on the banners on the back wall of the tower to get up to the 3rd floor.  There are vendors for Wizard, Enchanter, and Magician spells (including many which were previously research-only).  I think the pets are on a different vendor from the other spells.  I seem to recall the pet vendor was a Gnome, but I could be wrong.<br>
<br>
It's very easy to get to Katta now.  Just ask a friendly Wizard for a TL to Twilight Sea (and tip 10pp).  Then run to the back entrance of Katta, follow the runway around to the right, eventually you pop out near the bank.  Go up the stairs to the top level and I believe the Mage tower is ahead and to the left of you. <p><CENTER>
